oji\" />"},{"pid":"92663b95a21bd037ac90417c89b380f03471c43f","tid":348753,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉個條線入屋<br />\n係最近入屋位安個router<br />\n一係搵返個舊位 起返出黎</blockquote><br />\n老母話明線好核突，唔俾<br />\n<br />\n舊位起唔到，要拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53df2e0783be69ccdac3ed08955013762e46afe0","tid":348753,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拉個條線入屋<br />\n係最近入屋位安個router<br />\n一係搵返個舊位 起返出黎</blockquote><br />\n老母話明線好核突，唔俾<br />\n<br />\n舊位起唔到，要拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要拆晒成幅牆同櫃先得"},{"pid":"c0792fe24d08d32e704a434ea2f758c3055a196b","tid":348753,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T08:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你而家用緊咩呀？ADSL 6/8M 定 VDSL 30/100M????</blockquote><br />\n唔識，adsl掛，總之上網最快唔會過200kb/s <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157620e2b2ad2e58bb68ac2166cc5e7a7190cd72","tid":348753,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:53:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cda66de541214fdd425017a6697c461347e9ff5c","tid":348753,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人用和記？"},{"pid":"0781aacd31001512ae746e56238e1a8631da1bcd","tid":348753,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:41:12.000Z","msg":"和記會用返老電個電話制入屋，裝香港寬頻吧啦"},{"pid":"3b7ff6402ee8a9ed7179f851ce7d95fcaf1cb561","tid":348753,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:42:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你而家用緊咩呀？ADSL 6/8M 定 VDSL 30/100M????</blockquote><br />\n唔識，adsl掛，總之上網最快唔會過200kb/s <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n電聯有1.5m有更快的 但忘記了 你應該係1.5m 經電制入你屋企"},{"pid":"b22338833964cb3d7732ee428377b5c5ded49c1b","tid":348753,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T18:56:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>和記會用返老電個電話制入屋，裝香港寬頻吧啦</blockquote><br />\n依家人地拉唔到線入屋啊，裝波波就唔洗拉線啊？"},{"pid":"f4b34ac66ce9300b38b0f21bbaeea6c206ea3e83","tid":348753,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:01:19.000Z","msg":"樓主，如果你果到收4G好，咪試下用sim router囉<br />\n速度會好過你依家，但價錢會貴啲<br />\n天線位有無改過啊，無就試下用天線入屋<br />\n屋企有無對講機？有又可以用果到出線<br />\n如果咩都改哂封咗舊位，又唔肯明線，咁你咪試上面個方法"},{"pid":"5db5ceff655db667219b31e9c38ffc144faff78f","tid":348753,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T19:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>和記會用返老電個電話制入屋，裝香港寬頻吧啦</blockquote><br />\n依家人地拉唔到線入屋啊，裝波波就唔洗拉線啊？</blockquote><br />\nI cable 唔洗拉"},{"pid":"94b054a1409ed1b79268a8cc85d869e349c89660","tid":348753,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T03:59:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你而家用緊咩呀？ADSL 6/8M 定 VDSL 30/100M????</blockquote><br />\n唔識，adsl掛，總之上網最快唔會過200kb/s <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n電聯有1.5m有更快的 但忘記了 你應該係1.5m 經電制入你屋企</blockquote><br />\n係經電制的，但真係上得好慢，200kb/s 已經係極限"},{"pid":"7b7511a7eb3be3bfc07c90213264b2ceebb6cde1","tid":348753,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主，如果你果到收4G好，咪試下用sim router囉<br />\n速度會好過你依家，但價錢會貴啲<br />\n天線位有無改過啊，無就試下用天線入屋<br />\n屋企有無對講機？有又可以用果到出線<br />\n如果咩都改哂封咗舊位，又唔肯明線，咁你咪試上面個方法</blockquote><br />\n呢個有諗住，上fb page 格過價，但俾屋企上網用嘅sim plan 其實座底要$300 真心有啲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天線入屋呢個方法未聽過，想問問巴打，原理係點樣？"},{"pid":"b178f649526680b18f1b5d6f1a2a0d80ad416c8b","tid":348753,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T04:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>和記會用返老電個電話制入屋，裝香港寬頻吧啦</blockquote><br />\n依家人地拉唔到線入屋啊，裝波波就唔洗拉線啊？</blockquote><br />\nI cable 唔洗拉</blockquote><br />\n屋企個光纖頭成個拆咗，要裝返的話要拆屋先搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab44079a6e55ed6fa2e9d499fceee2270c6ac22","tid":348753,"uid":99941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T08:08:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>和記會用返老電個電話制入屋，裝香港寬頻吧啦</blockquote><br />\n依家人地拉唔到線入屋啊，裝波波就唔洗拉線啊？</blockquote><br />\nI cable 唔洗拉</blockquote><br />\n屋企個光纖頭成個拆咗，要裝返的話要拆屋先搞得掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI cable 行電視天線位入屋 (好似係)"},{"pid":"620882ced6d8a645ce841b590ce74fabf169075b","tid":348753,"uid":134022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e5cc52922a8457654340beeff8dc9eac07a3a24","tid":348753,"uid":61482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T11:41:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08d254624bdc1622fa1d5eed64490f2fd4244bfd","tid":348753,"uid":53830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主，如果你果到收4G好，咪試下用sim router囉<br />\n速度會好過你依家，但價錢會貴啲<br />\n天線位有無改過啊，無就試下用天線入屋<br />\n屋企有無對講機？有又可以用果到出線<br />\n如果咩都改哂封咗舊位，又唔肯明線，咁你咪試上面個方法</blockquote><br />\n呢個有諗住，上fb page 格過價，但俾屋企上網用嘅sim plan 其實座底要$300 真心有啲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天線入屋呢個方法未聽過，想問問巴打，原理係點樣？</blockquote><br />\n唔係要你用i cable , 係由原本用電話socket果條喉<br />\n改由用天線果條喉黎穿線，前提係你天線個主位無封無改<br />\n但穿會難穿，因為天線線粗喉幼"},{"pid":"160d963af6de7e38ccded5c63a1d7ad576f136bc","tid":348753,"uid":133299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T